#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.121"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.121:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.121:0.2"
msgid "10. Dutiyagaṅgāpeyyālavagga"
msgstr "10. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.121:0.3"
msgid "121. Paṭhamasamuddaninnasutta"
msgstr "121. Slanting to the Ocean"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.41"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.121:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the ocean."

msgctxt "sn45.121:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold "
"path slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn45.121:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path slant, slope, "
"and incline to extinguishment?"

msgctxt "sn45.121:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which culminate, finish, and end in the deathless."

msgctxt "sn45.121:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path "
"slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.121:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
